{"tid":17844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"城門水塘掛假車牌失車墮坡　19歲女子被捕","createTime":"2016-12-02T03:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T03:37:53.000Z","uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d3dc73f476f2bd69858f3b2b2924fec6e7ba594e","tid":17844,"uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:37:53.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】一輛掛上懷疑偽製車牌的報失私家車，昨晚在荃灣城門水塘衝下山坡。司機及乘客事後逃去，警方之後在荃灣，以涉嫌使用虛假文書拘捕一名19歲女子，正追查兩名20歲的男司機及男乘客下落。<br />\n　　私家車昨晚近8時衝出路面，墮下約10米下的山坡，零件飛脫，有市民目睹車禍後，兩名男子爬出車廂逃去。<br />\n　　肇事私家車事後由拖車吊返路面。警方調查後證實是一輛失車，並發現私家車掛上懷疑偽製車牌，車上有一張不屬於涉事私家車的行車證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9F%8E%E9%96%80%E6%B0%B4%E5%A1%98%E6%8E%9B%E5%81%87%E8%BB%8A%E7%89%8C%E5%A4%B1%E8%BB%8A%E5%A2%AE%E5%9D%A1-19%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-023200718.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%259F%258E%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25A1%2598%25E6%258E%259B%25E5%2581%2587%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%2589%258C%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E5%259D%25A1-19%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-023200718.html&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=16004067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9F%8E%E9%96%80%E6%B0%B4%E5%A1%98%E6%8E%9B%E5%81%87%E8%BB%8A%E7%89%8C%E5%A4%B1%E8%BB%8A%E5%A2%AE%E5%9D%A1-19%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-023200718.html</a><br />\n<br />\n咁沙膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}